            <title>[SOLR-8991] UI: Ping option doesn&apos;t update menu with response time if it&apos;s 0ms</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-8991</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The ping menu option for a core doesn&apos;t provide any useful feedback to hte user what it&apos;s doing when the ping response time is 0ms.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
