                            <comment id="15242050" author="jira-bot" created="Thu, 14 Apr 2016 22:25:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1e7f3408978d18fd3a7cfa4d11dc2f499536c781 in lucene-solr&apos;s branch refs/heads/branch_6_0 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=upayavira&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;upayavira&quot;&gt;upayavira&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
